  dialogueLines:
  - Taika!!!!
  - Oh, hi Emma. What are you doing here?
  - "The show won\u2019t start until the evening. "
  - You.. You asked me to come here, in your letter?
  - "You said you needed help! Come on, we\u2019re going home. "
  - ' What letter?'
  - " Emma, you\u2019re being silly. The Circus is my home now, why would I leave? "
  - " I don\u2019t know, something about \u2018The Ringleader isn\u2019t what he
    seems\u2019 kind of sent alarm bells going in my head!!"
  - 'The Ringleader is a nice man, Emma! I was just spooked on my first day, hahah~ '
  - But-
  - " I\u2019m fine! I love it here!"
  - 'Everyone does. '
  - '... '
  - " If you don\u2019t believe me, ask them! Have fun and walk around, maybe you
    want to stay here too~"
  - ...
  - Fine.
